[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    626[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      gender, age cohort, geography, insurance,            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    627[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      social-determinant flags)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    628[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial recruitment funnel by referral source      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    629[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial recruitment funnel by channel              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    630[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort prescreen-yield, handoff-rate,            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    631[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent-rate-from-handoff, randomized-rate-from-     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    632[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent (the longer-window outcomes accumulate as    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    633[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the trial progresses)                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    634[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort dashboards reviewed by the principal      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    635[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      investigator, the institutional research-            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    636[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      recruitment team, the sponsor's recruitment team,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    637[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and (where applicable) the diversity-action-plan-    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    638[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tracking team                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    639[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    640[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational telemetry]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    641[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation completion rate                         │
