[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    647[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation-coverage rate                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    648[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Novel-recruitment-language detection rate            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    649[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recommendation-pattern detection rate                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    650[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort metric slices                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    651[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    652[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sampled clinical-and-regulatory-quality review]        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    653[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Random sample plus targeted sample of escalations,   │
