[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    659[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      misclassification, citation-gap, vulnerability-      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    660[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      missed, vulnerability-false-positive)                │
