[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    666[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: audit trail, telemetry, learning signals,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    667[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    IRB-amendment proposals, content-revision proposals]   │
