[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 3: Handle the recruitment conversation with strict citation grounding.** This is the conversation core. Every trial-specific assertion is grounded in cited IRB-approved content. Every eligibility assertion is grounded in cited criterion-rule. The output-safety verifier detects novel-recruitment-language and regenerates or falls back. The conversation pattern reuses the LLM-with-tool-use orchestration from previous chapter 11 recipes with recruitment-specific tools.
