[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1878[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Recipe 4.7 (Care Management Program Enrollment):** Chapter 4. Patients identified as appropriate for trial recruitment based on care-management triggers can be warm-routed to the recruitment conversationalist.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1879[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Recipe 5.x (Entity Resolution / Record Linkage):** Chapter 5. Patient-record matching across the institution's EHR, HIE participation, and the trial's recruitment systems supports the identity-and-context loading.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1880[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Recipe 6.x (Cohort Analysis / Clustering):** Chapter 6. Population analytics support trial-eligibility-pool sizing and trial-recruitment-strategy planning.
